       <div class="content"> 
        <p><a href="http://blogs.westmont.edu/2014/08/13/researchers-lay-up-diet-tips-for-cagers/"><img src="http://blogs.westmont.edu/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/GreggAfmanJamesBetts-168x168-1407959306.jpg" width="84" height="84" alt="Drs. Gregg Afman and James Betts"></a><span class="text">An international collaboration of sports scientists, including researchers from Westmont College, have developed new nutritional practices that could help NBA players prepare for the upcoming season. </span> <a href="http://blogs.westmont.edu/2014/08/13/researchers-lay-up-diet-tips-for-cagers/">[more]</a></p> 
